  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nPeerManager PR https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/2142 changed the ping frequency to match Lighthouse's (once per 15s), which is faster than what we previously had (once per epoch).\r\n\r\nPrater genesis logs show a lot a failed ping requests, broken streams and timeouts.\r\n\r\nSeeing that our node is extremely overloaded, benchmark the cost of pinging 25 peers every 15 seconds and reduce if necessary.\r\n",
